WEBVTT

00:00:27.365 --> 00:00:30.789
(Laughter)

00:00:30.813 --> 00:00:32.407
Alright, alright.

00:00:32.954 --> 00:00:36.771
And maybe you're thinking,
"Well, it won't be me."

00:00:37.350 --> 00:00:40.735
Then, OK. You are a caregiver.

00:00:41.388 --> 00:00:42.552
So --

00:00:42.576 --> 00:00:45.448
(Laughter)

00:00:45.472 --> 00:00:46.829
so in some way,

00:00:46.853 --> 00:00:50.497
this terrifying disease
is likely to affect us all.

00:00:50.933 --> 00:00:53.947
Part of the fear around Alzheimer's
stems from the sense

00:00:53.971 --> 00:00:56.385
that there's nothing we can do about it.

00:00:56.409 --> 00:01:01.534
Despite decades of research, we still
have no disease-modifying treatment